This directory contains the minimum subset of boost
just enough to make Spirit work. Packaging instructions:

1. Rename the "boost" directory to "miniboost"
2. Add a new "boost" directory.
3. Move "spirit.hpp" and the "spirit" directory from the
   miniboost directory to the new "boost" directory.
4. Move the contents of "mini-boost-dir" directory into 
   the "miniboost" directory.
5. Move the contents of "top-level-dir" directory into 
   the top level directory.
6. Delete this readme, "top-level-dir" and "mini-boost-dir".
7. Remove all CVS artifacts
8. Compress and release.

